item.title: 【Albums (lossless)】ALAC - Violetta / TINI: IL CONCERTO (Live in Milan) ITALIAN VERSION (Rare) [Disney ALAC 16Bit/44.1kHz]
item.description:
Violetta is a Disney Channel latin telenovela broadcasted in all the Disney Channels excepting the U.S. and Asia, Violetta toured in Latin America & Europe outgrossing Hannah Montana’s tours, though later Violetta was outgrossed by Soy Luna.

This is an exclusive release for Italy, it’s not the same album released in the rest of the world which was recorded at the Gran Rex Theater in Argentina, this one was recorded in Milan, Italy on January 3 & 4, 2014 at the Unipol Forum in front of a crowd of 15,800 italian and european fans

Contains bonus tracks sang in italian by the original members of the cast
